Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.87,0:00:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.61,0:00:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.29,0:00:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.23,0:00:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.87,0:00:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.64,0:00:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.41,0:00:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.88,0:00:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.99,0:01:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.53,0:01:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.00,0:01:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.67,0:01:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.14,0:01:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.65,0:01:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吵喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.84,0:01:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,安靜一點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上你明明吵成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要鬧了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要睡到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是什麼時候來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.09,0:02:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還敢問?竟然沒有來接我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.42,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是今天嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.99,0:02:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.54,0:02:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N妳覺得我們家裕作怎麼樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.02,0:02:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會覺得有點靠不住?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不會啊,而且他很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.56,0:02:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的姪女和他的女朋友\N好像都很喜歡他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.97,0:02:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,她叫七尾小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.87,0:02:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#34戀愛必須強硬!\N由加里奶奶以金牙決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.42,0:03:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,妳是五代的奶奶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.03,0:03:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面,我叫七尾小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,這個女孩很可愛嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.87,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,這是妳要的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這本,這是一本很難的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且很貴,我一直買不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是寫報告突然要用到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔,真不愧是五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.62,0:03:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦,只是碰巧找到而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別騙了,明明是在來的途中\N在路邊的書店買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真的很愛面子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.10,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了女生面前,馬上開始裝帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是特地幫我去找這本書的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,對不起喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然帶我奶奶來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.35,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說,我很高興\N你願意把我介紹給你的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,沒有那麼正式啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意嫁來我們家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳怎麼又說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你喜歡的是別人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有說不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.32,0:04:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人說話很不乾脆吧\N他個性比較害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會每天幫奶奶搥背的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.93,0:04:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳\N對了,你們不用吻別嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一起出去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去見小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.86,0:05:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個好女孩\N一定要娶來當裕作的老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,管理員很忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打擾了你們的幽會\N你很不甘願嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼沒有吻她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.38,0:05:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N幹嘛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底喜歡誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小津江?還是管理員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.55,0:05:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然問我這個啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做個決定!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.32,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.03,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能一次娶兩個人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.89,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說,我還是個學生耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼關係\N喜歡就要在一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.07,0:06:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才是男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.70,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選老婆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃開閃開,老婆婆要過路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不相干的人請走開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點決定吧,這是個好機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.78,0:06:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正他一個人是下不了決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些人啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有意思的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.93,0:06:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得選擇小津江比較保險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她沒有女人味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人味馬上就會有的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家坐下來說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊喝酒一邊決定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好極了,我來陪你們喝兩杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,怎麼沒有杯子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杯子在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶妳坐著,我來幫妳拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選老婆大會\N大家一起選就不用怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選老婆,選老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,選你喜歡吃的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,不能一次選兩個\N這樣會吃壞肚子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.97,0:07:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.67,0:08:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看,要選哪一個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.63,0:08:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,融化掉了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你不快點選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.19,0:08:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙跟以前一樣\N一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連選個老婆都猶豫不決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.44,0:09:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只好再住幾天囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.12,0:09:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然管理員說\N他只是個普通朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.99,0:09:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個男的,可是很熱情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也很在意這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作也見過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,經常見到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.93,0:09:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個大白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶要不要也去看一看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(時鐘坡網球俱樂部)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個大帥哥耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好氣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,休息10分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,網球有趣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個蠻配的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是音無小姐的朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是音無小姐的奶奶嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.82,0:10:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狠角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這麼照顧我孫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,我才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.54,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想對你多了解一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正討好她也沒有損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.91,0:11:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空的話,改天到我家來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.35,0:11:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帶我的孫子去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以\N對不對?音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是妳的奶奶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,她是五代的奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.15,0:11:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,他真是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,對於女性的要求\N他絕對不會拒絕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個禮拜六,開車來接我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.73,0:12:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去三鷹家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要招待我們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要我跟去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多認識一下情敵\N對你又沒有損失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員說她也會去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳想把我拿來當笑柄嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.65,0:12:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會讓我們體驗到\N我們的貧富差距有多大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.89,0:12:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係\N這樣你也能死心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要死心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就去吧,好好地掌握實際狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(三鷹家)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.60,0:13:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,真的好豪華喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.61,0:13:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你們是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣了,隨便坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家整理得好乾淨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.99,0:13:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個禮拜一次\N請傭人來打掃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是用你的薪水租的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,大概二十萬左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你的房間簡直天壤之別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就料到了\N反正我們家很窮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看你又說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱片借我看一下,好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,儘管看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要放些音樂來聽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也聽歌劇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我也看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.54,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,蠻不錯的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,管理員,這張唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.38,0:14:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次我們一起聽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個寂靜的夜晚\N月色好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳稍微有點喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有喝醉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,有有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.86,0:14:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那時候真的好好笑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.99,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美喝醉時\N歌聲就會變得五音不全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐\N我有樣東西很想讓妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.88,0:15:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.69,0:15:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著網球的遠征\N到處蒐集回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.30,0:15:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你有這種嗜好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.47,0:15:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是啦\N買著買著就越來越多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是在拿坡里的跳蚤市場買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.54,0:15:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外這一個我記得是\N去阿姆斯特丹的時候買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位小姐好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳開了我的抽屜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.79,0:16:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏在裡面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,居然還摟著人家的肩膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧,就當著管理員的面\N解釋一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.44,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實,我以前跟這女孩住在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狠角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有證據能證明她是你妹妹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?\N常常有人說我們長得很像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.57,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牙齒也會發亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了好多東西,肚子也餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.87,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去做飯來吃吧\N反正這裡有好多食材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳打開我的冰箱看過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳去坐著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我們兩個就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.49,0:17:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嫌老人家礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問,胡椒在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.84,0:17:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個廚房用起來好方便喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我有考慮到\N我未來妻子的使用方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,幫我去買個醬汁好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.27,0:17:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我去買?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼事都沒做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.41,0:17:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點去買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思喔,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉,我到底在幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.08,0:18:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳在這裡幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.81,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.27,0:19:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹那傢伙如果敢對管理員亂來\N我絕對饒不了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.45,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.89,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,奶奶,妳到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到樓下去接裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.23,0:19:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好,因為妳突然不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.70,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,剛剛才回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人傷腦筋\N害我們擔心得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.14,0:20:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,你的料理總是這麼好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有妳的幫忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.38,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,這道菜叫作\N酸奶油牛肉洋蔥蘑菇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝免費的酒,吃免費的大餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.87,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.74,0:21:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那麼嚴重的貧富差距\N你死心了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才不會死心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的跟你爺爺一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.35,0:21:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實,除了你爺爺\N還有個有錢的男人向我求過婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少騙人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是個好男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像三鷹教練一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.01,0:21:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候你爺爺也跟你一樣\N顯得有點焦慮不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果我甩了那個帥哥\N選擇了你爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是為什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.68,0:22:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我看到你爺爺那副\N拼死拼活的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.09,0:22:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這個男人會愛我一輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.59,0:22:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起金錢,能夠被人愛\N對女人才是最幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.43,0:22:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.65,0:22:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了,原來奶奶想說這番話\N才叫我去三鷹他家的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.32,0:22:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我現在後悔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.86,0:22:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是一時的意亂情迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.36,0:22:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果愛情是一樣的話\N應該毫不猶豫選擇多金的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.43,0:22:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳這樣也算是自家人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.50,0:22:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?\N現在終於死心了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.81,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.81,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是怎麼了?\N這次怎麼兩人一起消失?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.41,0:23:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.72,0:23:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,這傢伙說他要死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.49,0:23:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死心什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.19,0:23:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.76,0:23:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要對我說,對管理員說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.49,0:23:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要對什麼死心?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.60,0:23:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.64,0:23:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙太不乾脆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.68,0:23:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.88,0:23:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續多住幾天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.26,0:23:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由加里奶奶幫我跟五代\N計劃了一個約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.06,0:23:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照著奶奶的行程進行的約會\N究竟會變得如何呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.23,0:23:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.87,0:24:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「追蹤大作戰!\N瞄準響子和五代的約會」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.27,0:24:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我想太多嗎?\N總覺得感到有股陰謀的氣息…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.15,0:24:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.49,0:24:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.54,0:24:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.24,0:24:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.82,0:24:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.09,0:24:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.96,0:24:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.80,0:25:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.93,0:25:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
